\r\nBest Entry by a Student under 16 years<br />\r\nBest Edited Entry <br />\r\nMost Humorous Entry Best Entry by a Student age 16 - 19 years<br />\r\nBest Canadian Entry <br />\r\nBest Documentary Entry <br />\r\nBest Entry by a Student age 20 and over',1,'','Since 1969 Movie Makers from more than forty nations have participated','','',1,'2003-08-01','');
