INSERT INTO fests VALUES (1191,'Albert International Wildlife Film Festival','','','Albert','','','Festival International du Film Animalier','55 rue de Birmingham','Albert','France','80300','33 3 22 75 48 88','33 3 22 75 48 88','fifa@dyadel.net','http://fifa.dyadel.net','','http://perso.wanadoo.fr/fifa-albert/entries.htm','0000-00-00','2003-10-15','0000-00-00','2004-03-20','2004-03-28','','Created in 1991, this wildlife festival seeks to achieve a cultural challenge underlining a passion for fishing, hunting and for nature through films.Albert&#039;s Festival takes place every year in March. It lasts eight days, in front of an audience and in a modern<br />\r\ntheatre equiped with all the appliances and technique necessary to such a huge event. This theatre called <br />\r\n&quot; Thtre du Jeu de Paume &quot; stands in the city centre, next to a big car park and has six hundred seats <br />\r\navailable.','','','','France','','',NULL,'Europe',0,'',0,0,0,'GRAND PRIX, Getting to know and protecting Wildlife Prize , Getting to know and protecting waterlife Prize, Prize for the relationship between Man and Animal , Prize for the best scientific Film ,  Spcial Jury Prize, Public Special Prize, Amateur Prize, Getting to know and protecting the European Wildlife Prize, Spcial Prize for the best Picture , Spcial Prize for the best Scenario, Spcial Prize for the best Sountrack, Spcial Prize for the best  Editing<br />\r\n<br />\r\n',1,'','The first year, Albert&#039;s Festival was a venture full of surprises and discoveries and, as years went by, it quickly<br />\r\nbecame an event which couldn&#039;t be ignored in the world of animal films. It is now greatly considered by directors<br />\r\nand producers on the five continents. ','There is a pre-inaugural evening devoted to a country and which shows its wildlife, its folore and<br />\r\nalso a preview of extracts from the films selected.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThere are evenings with precise themes : one devoted to hunting, one to fishing, one to the environment.<br />\r\nOn these occasions specific films are shown and special guests are invited.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAn official competition takes place in which each film selected is shown to an international jury composed<br />\r\nof people who are famous in the world of cinema, television, the press or in organisations specialized in <br />\r\nwildlife.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDuring the gala evening, the panel of judges, the producers and the directors who take part in the competition are introduced to the audience and so are prestigious guests of honour.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEvery day, there are special viewings for school children and the Wednesday afternoon is devoted<br />\r\nto children with films, workshops, games, and animal quizzes.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFor a whole week, there are exhibitions linked to animals with sculptors, painters, photographers, <br />\r\ntaxidermists, aquariums and multimedia columns.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe festival ends up with the panel of judges giving their awards list in front of personalities and the<br />\r\naudience. Finally, the best film of the year is shown to the audience.<br />\r\n','',1,'2003-07-21','');
