INSERT INTO fests VALUES (1292,'Academia Film Olomouc','Palack University - Jesuits Convent','','Olomouc','771 47','420 68 563 1053','Palack University, Office AFO','Krizkovskeho 8','Olomouc','Czech Republic','771 47','420 68 563 1053','420 68 522 2802','urbasek@rupnw.upol.cz','http://www.upol.cz/afo2000/','','','0000-00-00','2003-05-20','0000-00-00','2003-09-29','2003-10-22','Each film or video programme registration for categories (A), (B) and (C) must be accompanied by a full dialogue/commentary script in English. Photographs and other promotional materials must be <br />\r\nenclosed. For the programmes in category (D), a description of operations (if necessary, an instruction manual) in English must be enclosed.','Academia Film Olomouc is an international festival of documentary, scientific, popular scientific, educational and multimedia programmesand exhibition of information technologies in the educational process.Topic of this year is on the road...','','','','Czech Republic','','Only films and video programmes less than two years old can be accepted into the International Competition. Participation in other festivals is no obstacle to participations in AFO 2003. <br />\r\n',NULL,'Europe',0,'',0,0,0,'The films and video programmes in the International Competition will be judged by an Intenational Jury appointed by the Festival President. The International Jury awards the prizes. It is entitled to award:<br />\r\nThe AFO Grand Prix 2003.<br />\r\nAn award in each category:<br />\r\n(A) Award for the best documentary;<br />\r\n(B) Award for the best scientific and popular-science programme; <br />\r\n(C) Award for the best educational programme;<br />\r\n(D) Award for the best multimedia programme.<br />\r\nThe special Evald Schorm Award for the best programme related to the arts.<br />\r\nThe Jury can recommend:<br />\r\nThe Mayor of Olomouc Award;<br />\r\nThe President of the Olomouc Region Award <br />\r\nand other prizes.<br />\r\nThe Students Jury can awa