INSERT INTO fests VALUES (1329,'Brussels International Festival of Fantasy Film','','','Belgium','','','rue de la Comptesse de Flandre 8','Gravin van Vlaanderenstraat 8','Brussels','Belgium','B-1020','32- 2- 201 1713','32 [0] 2 201 14 09','presse.festivals@skypro.be','http://www.bifff.org','http://www.bifff.org/fotos/banners/19.jpg','http://www.bifff.org/en/forms/','0000-00-00','2003-12-31','0000-00-00','2004-03-12','2004-03-17','','Ever since our foundation in 1979, we want to highlight a cinema of quality. Because you cannot separate cultural matters from social matters, we want to engage the larger public&#039;s interest for the social and cultural aspects of movies. We also try to punch through the sometimes elitist character of the cultural world and promote the distribution of this &quot;cinema of quality&quot;. To achieve this, PeyMey (PM) uses &quot;the power of the imagination&quot;. We want to innovate in the field of the organization and diffusion of cultural events. We offer our rich experience, our services and our capacities to any cultural manifestation that underwrites our objectives..','','','','Belgium','','',NULL,'Europe',0,'',400,105,0,'Range of prizes in the International Feature, European Feature, and International Short Film categories.',1,'International Body Painting Contest','Reveal and to valorise the cinematographic works of fantasy, science-fiction and thriller','The Festival has once again given proof of its great popularity by welcoming 60.257 spectators. Sixteen candidates coming from Belgium, France, Germany, Austria, the Netherlands New-Zealand and Ukraine participated at the International Body Painting Contest. The creations of 40 participants were presented at the Unusual Fashion Show. And the Ball of Vampires welcomed some 2000 visitors in fancy dress or with make up, who gathererd at the Caves de Cureghem.','',1,'2003-07-31','');
