INSERT INTO fests VALUES (1343,'Atlantic City Film Festival','','','Atlantic City','8401','609-347-0074','36 Mechanic Street, #2','','Absecon','NJ','8201','609-646-1640','609-646-1656','info@atlanticcityfilmfestival.com','http://www.atlanticcityfilmfestival.com','http://www.atlanticcityfilmfestival.com/images/header2_01.gif','http://www.atlanticcityfilmfestival.com/39.cfm','0000-00-00','2003-05-30','0000-00-00','2003-08-09','2003-08-16','Entries must include a three to four sentence synopsis of the work. The synopsis should be a clear and concise description of the plot and/or premise of the submission and may not exceed 100 words. <br />\r\nEntries must include a complete list of cast, credits and a self-addressed stamped postcard in order to confirm receipt. <br />\r\nAny news release materials (i.e., media kits, media releases, posters, additional images, etc.) must be submitted to the festival office at the time of acceptance. ','After six successful seasons, the Atlantic City Film Festival, through the vision of its creator and CEO Joseph Fedison, is now positioned for explosive growth to claim its rightful place on the map of the independent film world.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOur mission is to use a contemporary and historical, culturally diverse media exhibition, production, and discussion as a means to enrich and educate the public, foster community and offer intercultural perspectives. Each year the Festival showcases full-length features, foreign films, shorts and documentaries. ','','','','USA','North East','',NULL,'North America',0,'',0,0,0,'There will be awards for all categories: feature, documentaries, animation, shorts and student films. Certificates will also be presented to films/videos deserving special recognition. ',1,'Local venues and entertainment, including the Atlantic City Boardwalk, hotels, casinos and beaches make for a fun destination for the entire family.<br />\r\n','Showcases the talents of the latest and greatest filmmakers.','','',1,'2003-07-24','NJ');
